         logger.debug(`[GroupChat] Connected: ${userName} (socket=${socket.id}, user=${userId})`)
 
+        // HERMES_CUSTOM[GroupChatAutoJoin] BEGIN: auto-join user's visible rooms on connect
+        // so the socket receives live `message` events for unread tracking while the user
+        // is in the cockpit (not actively viewing any group room). Unread is in-memory on
+        // the client (resets on refresh — accepted). We emit `unread_sync` with the last
